Imports metadata provided by an MSOrganizer EXCEL template

Source: R/read_metadata.R
import_MSOrganizerXLM.Rd

Imports metadata provided by an MSOrganizer EXCEL template

Usage

import_MSOrganizerXLM(filename, trim_ws = TRUE)

Arguments

filename

File path of the MSOrganizer EXCEL template (*.xlm)

trim_ws

Trim all white spaces and double spaces

Value

A list of tibbles with different metadata

Examples

library(SLINGtools)

data_file_path <- system.file("extdata",
  "Testdata_Lipidomics_MHQuant_Detailed.csv", package = "SLINGtools")
d <- read_MassHunterCSV(data_file_path)
